{"tid":583903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[2016]泛民：若楊岳橋守不住關鍵一席，議事規則將被修改！","createTime":"2018-03-07T11:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T05:36:47.000Z","uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2257b815e8220a4d4cbf4608325a3e4368ca2a1d","tid":583903,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:32:57.000Z","msg":"建制派修改議事規則 民主派將「輸晒」<br />\n<br />\n公民黨黨魁梁家傑表示，對旺角事件感到傷感，但梁振英藉機會挑起政治鬥爭，全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳昨日更稱應盡快就《基本法》23條立法，露出孤狸尾巴。<br />\n<br />\n梁家傑續指，現時地區直選議席中，泛民與建制派各有17席，若建制派在是次補選多取一席，便可橫行霸道，修改《議事規則》。工黨立法會議員張超雄指，如果建制派成功修改《議事規則》，阻止民主派拉布，少眾將失去僅有的發聲機會，「支持民主派的人今次不投票，我哋可能會輸晒」。<br />\n<br />\n前立法會議員吳靄儀表示，旺角事件發生正是源於政府有恃無恐，如果建制派在議會得勢，香港人更加絕望，難以估計未來會發生甚麼事。社民連立法會議員梁國雄亦呼籲「全投楊岳橋，激死梁振英！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1040633\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1040633&d=yfStLp%2FTRVbgmmFJcqg0PzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=a5622295\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1040633&h=54beccc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1040633</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋：2020，要取下36度過半數議席！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/193105_e33b16c7a9bd21516734603b856353ff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F193105_e33b16c7a9bd21516734603b856353ff.png&h=a9edc7fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d11331ce6f2194e07c86cf486d74c5a039a21f55","tid":583903,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8db37cffb5f77ec264cc285dbef1e4dc32ccf4","tid":583903,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"